# Ethereum Upgrade Process Documentation

_This document captures how Ethereum protocol upgrades actually work in practice — the unwritten rules, tribal knowledge, and coordination patterns that aren't formally documented elsewhere. It was created in October 2025 through an in-depth Q&A between nixo and ChatGPT, based on her understanding of the ACD process from working on protocol coordination. It's maintained as a living reference and updated as the process evolves._

---

## Core Principles

- Ethereum upgrades happen in public
- The process is collaborative across multiple client teams
- Consensus is sought but not always formally recorded
- Documentation is improving but still has gaps
- **Recency is critical** - the most recent information is the most up-to-date, as directions can change drastically in just a couple of weeks

